title: The 4 Biggest Travel Mistakes of Single Men (Episode 209)
description:
Show Notes:
2:48 Maria introduction
3:14 Show agenda
4:00 Questions from leverage group members
4:37 Why hooking up while traveling leads to higher quality experiences
6:28 Pros and cons of traveling for single guys
8:17 What about singe women?
8:45 Mistake 1 - hitting on other travelers
9:13 Don’t tell people you are leaving soon
11:14 Mistake 2 - traveling to visit a girl in hopes of hooking up
18:14 So many things can go wrong if you do this
21:32 Visiting women gives them control, and you none
22:33 Benefits of meeting at a neutral place
23:18 How long to stay
25:18 Mistake 3 - traveling solo if you are already lonely
28:04 How to find a wingman
31:15 Where to go, where not to go and how to decide
34:34 Smaller cities off the beaten path are better options that big popular places
36:39 Recommendations from the experienced traveler
39:12 Mistake 4 - Cruises and all inclusives
42:10 Hostels - good idea or bad idea?
40:51 Couchsrurfer and show around
41:36 Travel hacking tips, advice and best practices
